Title: Re-Entry
Plot: Charlie Crews and Dani Reese try to narrow down the list of suspects when a retired NASA pilot is shot mid-flight; Crews tries to remember who shot him.
GuestStars: Kayren Butler, Josh Randall, Richard Speight Jr., Alisha Snider, John Brantley Cole Jr., J.R. Nutt, Rajni Kareer, Jesse Bean, Kevin Indio Copeland, David Ury, Ed Corbin, J. Patrick McCormack
